{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_01","textHome":"什么？如果想组个魔法少女好朋友@小队的话……抱歉，能去找别人吗？我啊，@已经决定无论什么时候，都只为自己使用@魔法了。在战场上碰面的话还请多指教。@赌上猎物……堂堂正正的比试吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_18","textHome":"我发现了。@玩到最后啊，乐谱都可以背下来了。@所以这个还能锻炼大脑哦。@怎么样？你也试着跳一曲吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_19","textHome":"嗯，我感觉到了，状态不错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_20","textHome":"这种感觉，真是不错……@不如去随便干一场吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_21","textHome":"看到和我一样为了傻事而许愿的家伙@我就气不打一处来。不过……@像我一样的人……我是没法放着不管的啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_22","textHome":"已经许过愿的事就没法回头了。@所以我也希望……那些为了他人@而成为魔法少女的人……@能迎来幸福的结局。@那样的话，我也算是得到拯救了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_23","textHome":"有为了他人而许愿，最后得到幸福的人……@也有为了自己而许愿……只落得悲惨下场的人……@所以……我不用去后悔那一天我许下的愿望。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_24","textHome":"没想到又见到你了。嗯？我这身打扮才不会@感冒啦。因为我有特殊的锻炼方法。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_25","textHome":"呼啊，还是好困……真没想到我会为了@狩猎魔女，啊不对，是为了@准备万圣节而睡眠不足。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_26","textHome":"啊—啊—啊—！虽说是在练习发声方法，@但我一个人也搞不明白啊。这样子能练习@好么……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_27","textHome":"糟糕，已经到这个时间了…再不去排练的话，@那家伙又要开始啰嗦了……啊——@剧本也要带上。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_03","textHome":"越是单纯的人……@是不是就越容易受伤啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_28","textHome":"不给糖就捣乱！试着说了一下感觉好羞耻……@好啦，我都说完了，快把糖果交出来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_29","textHome":"从参加剧团演出开始，我才第一次意识到@万圣节来了。街道的景色，也意外有了些@万圣节的气息。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_30","textHome":"接下来，差不多该去家周围要糖果了。准备@好了就赶快出发吧。我对恶作剧什么的@才没兴趣呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_31","textHome":"要打扮成这样去镜界吗？要是那里全都是@大灰狼的话，可是会被啊呜一口吃掉的哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":400}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_32","textHome":"幽灵和魔物现世的万圣夜……@我是不会输给它们的……@我要把所有的糖果都拿到手！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_33","textHome":"这件衣服，虽然那个人说赶时间做出来的话，@可能会做得很粗糙，不过我感觉@并没有很粗糙。倒不如说，@对尾巴的制作很是执着。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_34","textHome":"说到万圣节的话，不光是糖果，饭菜也很有@特色。我不挑食的，所以就统统端上来吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_35","textHome":"穿着这样的衣服演戏，已经是多久之前的@事情了……在我小时候好像经历过，@不过已经记不清楚了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_36","textHome":"啊，这个吗？这个是苹果糖哦。要吃一个吗？@这里还有很多哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_37","textHome":"这个奇怪的城市又有魔女又有传闻，看来我@已经被卷入了和城市里的这些家伙@联系在一起的传闻之中了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_04","textHome":"不知道已经多久……@没有在这么时髦的饭店里吃饭了啊？@真好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_38","textHome":"虽然不记得我和那家伙说了什么了，那个叫@花凛的家伙，通过表演也收获了成长和喜悦。@她能够满足就是最好的了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_39","textHome":"穿着这件衣服，手脚虽然很冷，身体还有腰@周围却都是毛茸茸的，感觉很暖和。不过，@这是我的衣服所以我可不会让你碰的哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_40","textHome":"像这样大家一起围在一个桌子上吃饭的活动，@也让我想起了以前的一些回忆。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_02_41","textHome":"如果能从这块葡萄干蛋糕里吃出戒指的话，@就会有很好的结婚运，我的话不需要那种东西，@只要能让我吃蛋糕就够了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_42","textHome":"那么就放手大干一场吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_43","textHome":"这场胜利归我了。"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_44","textHome":"战果很不错！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_45","textHome":"好啦，要吃什么呢——"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_46","textHome":"打败敌人了！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_63","textHome":"交给我吧！这里就由我来解决！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_05","textHome":"竟然送我花……呵呵。@我真是遇到了可爱的魔女啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_64","textHome":"就用这招结束这场战斗……！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_65","textHome":"别在我眼前跳来跳去了，蠢货！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_66","textHome":"就用这招让你闭嘴……！盟神抉枪!!@哈啊啊啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_02","textHome":"我是佐仓杏子，幸会。@想和我一起战斗的话，就请我吃顿晚饭吧？@……开个玩笑。午饭就可以啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200600}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_13","textHome":"嗯，感觉还算不错。就这样继续吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_14","textHome":"好！到了这一步，@就该考虑下个阶段该怎么办了，对吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_15","textHome":"每个人都有不同的故事……@那么，这就是我的故事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_16","textHome":"我的性格就是要做就要做到最好。@就算是最高难度我也要完美通关。@哈？当然是在说跳舞机啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_17","textHome":"因为要追上不断从上面掉下来的音符，@所以我的动态视力也得到了锻炼，@对战斗也会有帮助哦。@嗯，说的就是跳舞机。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200600,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}